Class OwnerModule<C extends org.aeonbits.owner.Config>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.inject.AbstractModule
      • hm.binkley.inject.OwnerModule<C>
  • Type Parameters:
    C - the config type
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.google.inject.Module

    public final class OwnerModule<C extends org.aeonbits.owner.Config>
extends com.google.inject.AbstractModule
    OwnerModule is light-weight wiring of an OWNER API config instance into Guice. Guice does not support generic provider methods; each config needs to be separately configured.
    Author:
    B. K. Oxley (binkley)
